<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 40px;
      color: #000;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px double #000;
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 5px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .header h2 {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 5px 0;
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    .notice-box {
      border: 2px solid #000;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .meta-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .meta-table td, .meta-table th {
      border: 1px solid #333;
      padding: 8px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .meta-table th {
      background: #e0e0e0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .section {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: underline;
      margin: 15px 0 10px 0;
    }
    table.spec-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    table.spec-table td, table.spec-table th {
      border: 1px solid #444;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    table.spec-table th {
      background: #d0d0d0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 30px;
      left: 40px;
      right: 40px;
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #666;
      border-top: 1px solid #999;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }
    ul {
      margin: 5px 0;
      padding-left: 25px;
    }
    .stamp {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 100px;
      right: 60px;
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border: 2px solid #666;
      border-radius: 60px;
      opacity: 0.3;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transform: rotate(-15deg);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="stamp">OFFICIAL<br>DOCUMENT</div>
  
  <div class="header">
    <h1>{{organisation}}</h1>
    <h2>NOTICE INVITING TENDER (NIT)</h2>
    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">Tender No: <strong>{{tender_id}}</strong></div>
  </div>

  <div class="notice-box">
    <strong>Subject:</strong> {{title}}<br>
    <strong>Material Category:</strong> {{product_category}}<br>
    <strong>Location:</strong> {{city}}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">1. TENDER INFORMATION</div>
    <table class="meta-table">
      <tr>
        <th>Particulars</th>
        <th>Details</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Tender Reference No.</td>
        <td>{{tender_id}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Publication Date</td>
        <td>{{publish_date}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Bid Submission Deadline</td>
        <td>{{due_date}} (2:00 PM IST)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Estimated Value</td>
        <td>₹ {{formatCurrency estimated_cost_inr}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Delivery Location</td>
        <td>{{city}}</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">2. SCOPE OF WORK</div>
    <p>The {{organisation}} invites sealed bids from eligible vendors for the supply of <strong>{{material}}</strong> as per the technical specifications detailed below.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">3. TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS</div>
    <table class="spec-table">
      <tr>
        <th>S.No.</th>
        <th>Description</th>
        <th>Specification</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>1</td>
        <td>Material Type</td>
        <td>{{material}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>2</td>
        <td>Category</td>
        <td>{{product_category}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>3</td>
        <td>Standards Compliance</td>
        <td>IS 7098 (Part 1 & 2), IEC 60502, BIS certified</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>4</td>
        <td>Conductor Material</td>
        <td>Electrolytic Grade Copper, Class 2 stranded</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>5</td>
        <td>Insulation</td>
        <td>XLPE (Cross-linked Polyethylene), Type ST2</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>6</td>
        <td>Voltage Rating</td>
        <td>1.1 kV / 11 kV (as applicable)</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">4. ELIGIBILITY CRITERIA</div>
    <p>Bidders must satisfy the following conditions:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Must have executed at least THREE (3) similar orders in the last FIVE (5) years with Central/State Government entities or PSUs</li>
      <li>Average annual turnover of minimum ₹ 10 Crores in the last 3 financial years</li>
      <li>Valid ISO 9001:2015 certification for quality management</li>
      <li>Type test reports from NABL accredited laboratories</li>
      <li>Manufacturing facility with minimum 500 MT/month capacity</li>
      <li>No ongoing litigation or blacklisting by any Government department</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">5. COMMERCIAL TERMS</div>
    <table class="meta-table">
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Earnest Money Deposit (EMD)</strong></td>
        <td>₹ {{calculateEMD estimated_cost_inr}} (2% of estimated value)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Tender Fee</strong></td>
        <td>₹ 2,950/- (Non-refundable)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Bid Validity</strong></td>
        <td>120 days from bid opening date</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Payment Terms</strong></td>
        <td>80% against delivery, 20% after installation & commissioning</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Delivery Period</strong></td>
        <td>60 days from date of Purchase Order</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Warranty</strong></td>
        <td>24 months from date of commissioning</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">6. CONTACT INFORMATION</div>
    <p>
      <strong>For Technical Queries:</strong> {{contact_person}}<br>
      <strong>Email:</strong> {{contact_email}}<br>
      <strong>Phone:</strong> {{contact_phone}}<br>
      <strong>Address:</strong> {{organisation}}, {{city}}
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    This is an auto-generated tender document. Seal and authorized signature required. Page 1 of 1 | Tender {{tender_id}}
  </div>
</body>
</html>